	ficance. \\n    Guided Poetry writing activities\\n    Personal Universe D
	eck exercises\\n    Postcard-making/collage table\\n    Park history/nativ
	e flora\\n    Youth-led programming (Cascadia 2050!) \\nEvent Dates & Loca
	tions\\nApril 1\\\, 2026 — 6PM–8PM — yəhaw̓’ Indigenous Creatives Collecti
	ve\\nApril 18\\\, 2026 — 11AM–1PM — Kubota Garden\\nApril 25\\\, 2026 — 11
	AM–1PM — Be’er Sheva Park for a blessing of Mapes Creek\\nMay 2\\\, 2026 —
